 diminuer le taux d’arrêts maladie.</p>","_id":"1acdffd"},{"_id":"cd2cc90","tab_title":"Médecine","tab_content":"<p>En médecine, l’exosquelette est une ossature artificielle qui est portée à l’extérieur du corps humain. Il a alors pour rôle de compenser une ou plusieurs anomalies ou infirmités physiques. Il peut ainsi permettre à une personne handicapée de marcher.<br />Il peut aussi servir à la rééducation en favorisant l’apprentissage de gestes et de mouvements ou l’adoption de postures.</p>"},{"_id":"89617ec","tab_title":"Sport","tab_content":"<p>Chez les sportifs, les exosquelettes peuvent être employés afin de fournir une résistance au mouvement susceptible de favoriser le développement de la musculation et de la rapidité.</p>"}],"tab_typography_typography":"custom","tab_typography_font_family":"Arial","tab_typography_font_size":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"tab_typography_font_size_tablet":{"unit":"em","size":"","sizes":[]},"tab_typography_font_size_mobile":{"unit":"em","size":"","sizes":[]},"tab_typography_font_weight":"500","content_color":"#F1F1F1","content_typography_typography":"custom","content_typography_font_family":"Sura","content_typography_font_size":{"unit":"em","size":1.2,"sizes":[]},"content_typography_font_size_tablet":{"unit":"em","size":"","sizes":[]},"content_typography_font_size_mobile":{"unit":"em","size":"","sizes":[]},"content_typography_font_weight":"500","content_typography_text_transform":"none","content_typography_font_style":"normal","content_typography_letter_spacing":{"unit":"px","size":1.2,"sizes":[]}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"tabs"},{"id":"104ee92","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"Catégorie d'exosquelettes","header_size":"h1","align":"center","title_color":"#6EE480","typography_typography":"custom","typography_font_family":"Times New Roman","typography_font_size":{"unit":"em","size":3,"sizes":[]},"typography_font_size_tablet":{"unit":"em","size":"","sizes":[]},"typography_font_size_mobile":{"unit":"em","size":"","